social_posts.post_text: V.I.P. (PS1) is SO BAD 😂 — V.I.P. was a super cheesy TV show staring Pamela Anderson that was so bad it was (kinda) good. I guess it fits that the PlayStation game would be similar! This is a weird mix of quick time events, mini games and a shooter. It’s pretty terrible but also worth a laugh. #playstation #PS1

The Game I paid the MOST $$$ to own! 😬 Neverwinter Nights was the first graphical MMORPG to come out and it was AOL exclusive on PC. Getting a copy today can cost a pretty penny, but I got mine back in 2016 and it was the MOST MONEY $$$ I ever paid for a single game.
